	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vir clarissime, heri dedi cuidam mercatori fascem literarum, quem ad te perferet; at hodie oblata est mihi occasio huiusce nuncii, qui recta <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileam</placeName> proficiscitur.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque iterum scribo atque illud ipsum mitto, quod in prioribus literis missi; nam si illae forte perirent, hae quidem non peribunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi hodie literas a fratribus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiae</placeName>, qui scribunt oratorem regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Poloniae</placeName> conquestum fuisse apud <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425" cert="high">Romanum</placeName> pontificem, quod non[n]ulli diffamaverint suum regem, quasi coeperit consentire doctrinae nostrae, addiditque eum esse paratum etiam sanguinem pro <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425" cert="high">Romana</placeName> ecclesia adversum nos defendenda profundere.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic res est.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea scribunt papam parare reformationem nescio quam, scilicet ut amputet occasionem, ne quis clamet in concilio.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Persecutio fervet mirum in modum; rogate pro fratribus illis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego ad vos cogito redire, imo necesse puto, ut redeam pro Christi causa et nunciem vobis multa, quae non ita possunt epistolis committi.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque dabo operam, ut cito veniam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Antichristus dedit negotium cuidam Parascito, ut ad meos libros respondeat, iamque respondit ad non[n]ullos, sed impie, sed inepte, sed impudenter.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum hoc monstro mihi erit aliquandiu certandum.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic meus <persName ref="p8312" cert="high">Cocleus</persName> futurus est.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio nescio quid regem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallorum</placeName> non libenter concilii celebrationi consentire, puto in odium Caesaris, qui ex concilio illud sperat commodum, ut tota <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germania</placeName> ei serviat.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Itali</placeName> pro certo habent fore, ut modo <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustae</placeName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18574">Philippus</persName> detur <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538">Carolo</persName> coadiutor et successor.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, frater in Christo, et deum roga pro me cum tota ecclesia.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluto d. <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvalterum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Bibliandrum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesnerum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p1214" cert="high">Frisium</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4091" cert="high">Zvinglium</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1888" cert="high">Lavaterum</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8459" cert="high">Otthonem</persName>, d. Iosiam.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deus vos servet a malo per Christum, dominum nostrum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l96" cert="high">Claven[n]ae</placeName>, 23. decembris 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">H[enrico] Bullingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
